sequenceDiagram
    participant K as Kafka Broker<br/>(3 partitions: P0 P1 P2)
    participant S1 as Summarizer-1
    participant S2 as Summarizer-2
    participant S3 as Summarizer-3 (new)

    Note over K,S2: Initial state — 2 consumers, 3 partitions
    K-->>S1: P0, P1 assigned
    K-->>S2: P2 assigned

    Note over K,S3: Summarizer-3 joins consumer group
    S3->>K: JoinGroup request

    Note over K,S3: CooperativeStickyAssignor — incremental rebalance
    K-->>S1: Revoke P1 only (keep P0)
    Note over S1: S1 continues processing P0
    Note over S2: S2 continues processing P2

    K-->>S3: Assign P1
    Note over K,S3: Final state — no processing gap

    Note over S1,S3: Steady state
    K-->>S1: P0
    K-->>S2: P2
    K-->>S3: P1
